<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
  </head>

  <body>
    <p>Dear Customer,</p>

    <p>
      We were unable to generate your account statement for
      <strong><%= @statement.from_date %> to <%= @statement.to_date %></strong>
      for account <strong><%= @statement.account_number %></strong>.
    </p>

    <% if @error.present? %>
      <p>
        <strong>Reason:</strong> <%= @error %>
      </p>
    <% end %>

    <p>
      Please try again later. If the issue persists, contact our support team (6070)
      and quote reference ID <strong><%= @statement.id %></strong>.
    </p>

    <p>
      Regards
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
